{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Encoding API","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Encoding_API","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Encoding_API\">Encoding API</a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Interfaces</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/TextDecoderStream\"><code>TextDecoderStream</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/TextEncoderStream\"><code>TextEncoderStream</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta é uma <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tecnologia experimental (en-US)</a></strong><br>Verifique a <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">tabela de compatibilidade entre Navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usar essa funcionalidade em produção.</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p>O&nbsp;<strong>Encoding API</strong> providência uma mecânismo para tratar textos em vários tipos de <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Glossary/character_encoding\">encode de caracteres</a>, incluindo encodes legados non-<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Glossary/UTF-8\">UTF-8</a></p>\n\n<p>A API provém de quatro interfaces: <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>,&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoderStream\"><code>TextDecoderStream</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> e <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoderStream\"><code>TextEncoderStream</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"interfaces","title":"Interfaces","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"index\" id=\"sect2\">\n<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoderStream\"><code>TextDecoderStream</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoderStream\"><code>TextEncoderStream</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"tutoriais_ferramentas","title":"Tutoriais &amp; ferramentas","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>O&nbsp;<a href=\"https://code.google.com/p/stringencoding/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">shim</a> permite usar essa interface em navegadores que não a suportam.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/Code_snippets/StringView\" title=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Typed_arrays/StringView\"><code>StringView</code></a> – Um C-like reperesentação de strings baseados em arrays tipados</li>\n</ul>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://encoding.spec.whatwg.org/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'Encoding' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">Encoding</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>Definição inicial.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>","titleAsText":"Tutoriais & ferramentas"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"TextDecoder","id":"textdecoder","isH3":true,"query":"api.TextDecoder","dataURL":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Encoding_API/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"TextEncoder","id":"textencoder","isH3":true,"query":"api.TextEncoder","dataURL":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Encoding_API/bcd-2.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Interfaces","id":"interfaces"},{"text":"Tutoriais &amp; ferramentas","id":"tutoriais_ferramentas"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"O Encoding API providência uma mecânismo para tratar textos em vários tipos de encode de caracteres, incluindo encodes legados non-UTF-8","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Encoding API","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Encoding API","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Encoding API","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"인코딩 API","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Encoding API","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/encoding_api","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/encoding_api/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/We